Original work
-------------
The toolkit (v0.1) was created by Matias Medina (TFG, Universitat de Lleida, 2025),
originally published at https://github.com/TheSmuks/k8s-sims (Apache-2.0). This
repository is the GCD-UdL continuation/fork; see CHANGELOG.md for changes.

Bundled third-party artifact
----------------------------
- modules/opensim/cmd : a pre-built binary of Alibaba OpenSimulator
  ("open-simulator"), https://github.com/alibaba/open-simulator (Apache-2.0).

Integrated simulators (built from source, NOT redistributed here)
-----------------------------------------------------------------
These tools are downloaded/built from their own upstream repositories by the
respective modules; their source is not included in this repository and remains
under their own licenses:
- KWOK — https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/kwok (Apache-2.0)
- Kubemark / kube-scheduler-simulator — https://github.com/kubernetes-sigs/... (Apache-2.0)
- SimKube — https://github.com/acrlabs/simkube (MIT)
- K8sSim (Volcano simulator) — https://github.com/LINC-BIT/k8sSimulator (Apache-2.0)
- pfn k8s-cluster-simulator — https://github.com/pfnet-research/k8s-cluster-simulator (Apache-2.0)

Workload traces
---------------
Datasets are derived from public cluster traces (Alibaba clusterdata; Google
cluster-data / Borg; Azure Public Dataset) under their respective terms; the
trace data itself is not redistributed here (see utils/trace-convert/).

